<div style="position:absolute;left:87.60px;top:0.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">…</span><span class="cls_007">いいえ、きれいじゃ</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_007">ありません。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:357.00px;top:1.20px" class="cls_013"><span class="cls_013">…</span><span class="cls_003">不</span><span class="cls_004">，</span><span class="cls_003">不乾淨。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:523.50px;top:0.00px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">課</span><span class="cls_006">:8 (</span><span class="cls_005">頁</span><span class="cls_006">:9/9)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.80px;top:42.00px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">３</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:40.20px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">な</span><span class="cls_003">形容詞 </span><span class="cls_007">な</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:139.80px;top:42.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">名詞</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:60.60px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">い</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:80.40px;top:62.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">形容詞</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:120.00px;top:60.60px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(～</span><span class="cls_007">い</span><span class="cls_002">)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:166.20px;top:62.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">名詞</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:80.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">形容詞放在名詞前面修飾名詞。</span><span class="cls_007">な</span><span class="cls_009">形容詞以「な」的形式接續名詞。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:129.00px;top:97.74px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">せん せい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:181.80px;top:97.74px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">しん せつ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:234.60px;top:97.74px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">せん せい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:101.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">⑦</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">ワント</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">先生は</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">親切な</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">先生です。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:357.00px;top:103.20px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">瓦特老師是親切的老師。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:91.80px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">ふ    じ  さん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:155.40px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">たか</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:195.00px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">やま</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:121.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">⑧</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">富士山は</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">高い</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">山です。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:357.00px;top:123.60px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">富士山是很高的山。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.80px;top:162.60px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">４ </span><span class="cls_002">.    </span><span class="cls_007">とても</span><span class="cls_002">／</span><span class="cls_007">あまり</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:182.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">「とても」和「あまり」都是程度副詞</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">修飾形容詞時放在形容詞前面。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:203.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">「とても」是</span><span class="cls_010">“</span><span class="cls_009">很</span><span class="cls_010">”</span><span class="cls_009">的意思</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">用在肯定句中</span><span class="cls_010">；</span><span class="cls_009">「あまり」和否定形併用</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">表</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:223.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">示</span><span class="cls_010">“</span><span class="cls_009">不太</span><span class="cls_010">”</span><span class="cls_009">的意思。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:208.20px;top:240.54px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">さむ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:244.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">⑨</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">ペキンは</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_007">とても</span><span class="cls_008">   </span><span class="cls_007">寒いです。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:357.00px;top:246.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">北京很冷。</span></div>
